|-
| '''VRChat SDK'''
| [[Special:MyLanguage/VRChat SDK|VRCSDK3]] (Avatar 3.0)
|-
| '''VR hardware'''
| A VR headset; [[Special:MyLanguage/Full-Body Tracking|full-body tracking]] hardware (e.g., Vive trackers) is recommended for full-body recording
|-
